<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1077301'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1077301'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #33 于:</strong> 2020-10-04, 周日 02:00:10 &#187;</div>
